'''Thomas Briggs''', aka '''Sirtom93''' is a typical [[16 year old]] [[Aspie]] [[Britfag]] from Attleborough: Quiet, socially withdrawn, [[ginger]], lover of all things ''[[Star Trek]]'', avid user of the forums at [[Jewgrounds]]. Thomas also happens to be a recently-[[fail|failed]] [[an hero]], who on March 17, 2009, posted a few provocative sentences at the [[forum|Jew-venile recreation center]] regarding his impending attempt to go all [[VT|medieval]] on his local high school, little-realizing he would end up [[v&]] [[in the ass]] by the actions of a series of [[unwarranted self importance|pretentious]], similarly-socially withdrawn, ''Star Trek''-loving [[White Knight]]ers and [[moralfags]] on [[Jewgrounds]].

==[[bel-air|Now this is the story,]]==

Before it all went to shit, young Thomas was just a [[loser|normal kid]]; a fan of harmless [[atheism|church-burning]] racist murderer [[Black_metal#Varg|Burzum]], a furious masturbator, a [[Communist]], and a self-acknowledged [[pedophile]] [http://www.newgrounds.com/bbs/topic/998472 sympathizer] who was attracted to [http://www.newgrounds.com/bbs/topic/893459 manga girls] and [http://www.newgrounds.com/bbs/topic/909269 underage females], including a [http://209.85.229.132/search?q=cache:rVf9EinzI-AJ:www.newgrounds.com/bbs/topic/1025820/1+site:www.newgrounds.com+sirtom93+%22young+girls%22&cd=1&hl=en&ct=clnk&gl=uk&client=firefox-a 13-year-old girl]. He apparently [[aspie|got bullied]] and [[stupid|hated school]], but found [[porn|solace]] online. He turned up at [[Lolicon|Newgrounds]] [[circlejerk|fan-meets]], traveling [[at least 100|over 100]] miles from [[Niger|Norwich]] to [[China|London]] so he could hang about with some [[pervert|guys from the internet.]]

