==[[bel-air|All about how]]==

[[Image:ThomasBriggs.png|thumb|So angsty!]]

[[Image:Sirtomspetrolcan.jpg|thumb|brb, school]]

[[Image:Image2.gif|thumb|An accurate portrayal of the events.]]

[[Image:SirTom-and-his-girlfriend.jpg|thumb|Sirtom93 and his 8 year old lover, caught at the scene.]]

Shit started at 10:40AM [[Britfag|GMT]] on the internet's favorite place for depressed [[13-year-old boy|teenage]] [[goth|goths]], [[hentai|Newgrounds]]. Ceremoniously presenting his devious plans to his favorite forum, and inanely chatting for fifteen minutes with his largely apathetic fellow forumgoers, before gaily skipping off to school, Sirtom93 put forth a picture of [[lie|stunning bravado]], the likes of which had nary been seen before. Confident in his ability to haul [[arse]], Tom tooled up in as impressive a manner as a Brit can - i.e., with household objects.

{{quote|Today at 11:30 GMT I will attack my school with arson and other forms of violence. Those bastards will pay. I have cans, matches, lighter, knives, compressed explosives. Shit will go down in flames.|Sirtom93 initiating his downfall.}}

''Praise be to Satan,'' thought Thomas as he departed. ''If a [[cho|lesser race]] could do it with two tiny fucking pistols, then goddamn if I can't do it with plastic knives and a half-gallon of gasoline.'' But before sirtom93 could make his grand departure for the [[columbine|victory lap]], the [[shitstorm]] had already begun to brew in his quickly-growing thread. He found himself on the receiving end of some verbal rape by last-ditch attention-seeking [[moralfags]], who ordered him to [[fail|call it all off]] in order save the planet[[111|!!11!]]. Belligerently confronting those who would question his noble mission, Sirtom93 proceeded to mock posters in the thread with the solemn prediction which would later [[pwn|haunt]] him:

{{quote|Going to school now. Have fun with your conscience and lack of police speed.|sirtom93, the shortsighted almost-an hero.}}

The [[Newgrounds|Jewgrounds]] forum, a particularly attractive location for [[Jeff Weise|school shooters]], has had quite an illustrious history of violent individuals bent on reaching the high score (See: [[Livecorpse]], [[Jeff Weise]]), and was quick to respond to the case. One particular [[nazi|moderator]] by the name of '''JP Neufield''' ('''[[gay|Rig]]''' on [[Newgrounds|Jewgrounds]]), was busy sipping his Manitoba tea (a sickening conglomeration of Syrup and Yaks' blood) one morning on the frontier of the [[Canada|Canadian]] wasteland, the tubes of his internets humming quietly in the background, when he happened across our near hero's thread. Upon seeing it, he [[shit bricks|shat bricks]], realizing it was his grand [[attention whore|attention-whoring]] opportunity of the century. Phoning up the police in Norwich, U.K., with a solemn 'EH?,' Neufield solidified his position amongst the ranks of the most epic enemies of the lulz. Another Jewgrounds mod, britfag <s>Dick</s>Deckheadtottie, went so far as to call the principal of Thomas' school, and others.

==Tom's life got flipped==
When Briggs arrived at school (tardy!), with gas canister in hand, he was taken aside, [[raep|searched]] and [[bondage|detained]] by the [[mod]]s of [[IRL]].

